Mwananchi Credit has been awarded for being the best land title-based financier at the fourth annual Real Estate Excellence Awards in Nairobi.   Head of Operations Edwin Kagiri (pictured, centre) said through its title loans product, landlords access credit without fully charging the property by using a simple title deed deposit and a rent repayment agreement deed. The product has enabled many property owners to take loans for renovations and other related expenses.      KTN Prime Full Bulletin Business 24th March 2016  Tatu city project infrastructure   The Stanlib Fahari Income Reit to be listed on the Nairobi securities exchange  By Dominic Omondi | 4 hours ago By Frankline Sunday | 4 hours ago By Wainaina Wambu | 4 hours ago By Dominic Omondi | 13 hours ago